name: Lay Down Your Burdens The Investment

metadata.name: Lay Down Your Burdens (The Investment), pt. 5
metadata.description:
“I go through cycles. I come back to the Cuban link my father gave me - precious metals being his literal investment - when I’m feeling it, or I pin my hair up in a cute way when I’m feeling it, or both. I think there will always be times where I am at ease with having my gender perceived and other times where I feel hyper aware of the scrutiny it brings. I don’t think I’ll arrive at any end point in my gender experience.”

Sequence Index: 5/5
